description:
The ECO PLUMA roll-up rapid door was developed with places where controlled temperatures are required in mind.
This solution stands out for being more economical than other rapid roll-up doors, while retaining the aluminium safe and a reinforcing rail, suitable for areas with low air pressure.
TUB90M8-MT motor with 230Vac power supply;
MC76 electronic control board with up, down and stop button;
MFE photocell set;
External push button
